From ab22d6ca459e4227349098078d43c3ddcea81270 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Fuat Yahsi <yahsifuat@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 27 Apr 2026 15:10:37 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] ci(workflow): sweep YAML degisiminde otomatik tetik
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Sadece bu workflow dosyasi degisirse 'push' tetiklenmesi ekledim
(paths filter ile). Sweep her commit'te degil, yalnizca workflow
guncellemelerinde otomatik kosar — debug/iyilestirme dongusunu
hizlandirir, manuel 'Run workflow' tikina gerek kalmaz.

Trivial bir yorum guncellemesi de bu trigger'i tetikler:
'Trigger note: ... rerun marker: 1' satiri sayac olarak kullanilabilir.
---
 .github/workflows/marketfiyati-sweep.yml | 11 +++++++++++
 1 file changed, 11 insertions(+)

diff --git a/.github/workflows/marketfiyati-sweep.yml b/.github/workflows/marketfiyati-sweep.yml
index 8046f8a..3f4f29e 100644
--- a/.github/workflows/marketfiyati-sweep.yml
+++ b/.github/workflows/marketfiyati-sweep.yml
@@ -16,8 +16,19 @@ name: Market Fiyati Sweep
 #
 # 2026-04-26 cutover: sok marketfiyati'dan cikarildi (~%0.9 coverage).
 # Bkz. parsers/sok_direct.py ve parsers/sok_marketfiyati.py.
+#
+# Trigger note: bu YAML her degistirildiginde push tetiklenmesi kolayligi
+# icin `push` filter eklendi. Sweep her commit'te degil, sadece bu workflow
+# dosyasi degisirse tetiklenir — workflow degisikliklerini hizli test
+# etmek icin. Trivial bir yorum guncellemesi (rerun marker: 1) bile
+# isabettir.
 
 on:
+  push:
+    branches:
+      - main
+    paths:
+      - ".github/workflows/marketfiyati-sweep.yml"
   workflow_dispatch:
     inputs:
       markets:
-- 
2.34.1

